Join us for the Boston Jogger Tour, presented by Marathon Sports and Hoka! We're running the streets throughout the fall season. Come to each event for some fun, custom swag, raffles, and more! We'll celebrate the final run at Sam Adams - all paces welcome! Here's the full list of our event series:


Marathon Sports Boston 9/18 6:30PM


Marathon Sports Wellesley 10/16 6:30PM


Marathon Sports Cambridge 10/30 6:30PM


Marathon Sports Brookline 11/7 6:30PM


Celebration Run Party at Sam Adams 11/23 10AM
Samuel Adams Boston Brewery 30 Germania Street Boston, MA 02130
